    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "荒れ屋敷の前で"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "annotated",
          "text": "月の光が雲の間からほどけるころ",
          "reading": "つきのひかりが くものあいだから ほどけるころ",
          "language": "ja",
          "noteIds": ["note-moonlight"]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", a lone "
        },
        {
          "type": "annotated",
          "text": "旅人",
          "reading": "たびびと",
          "language": "ja",
          "noteIds": ["note-traveler"]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " arrived before an "
        },
        {
          "type": "annotated",
          "text": "荒れ屋敷",
          "reading": "あれやしき",
          "language": "ja",
          "noteIds": ["note-residence"]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". "
        },
        {
          "type": "annotated",
          "text": "葦は破れた門に触れ",
          "reading": "あしは やぶれたもんに ふれ",
          "language": "ja",
          "noteIds": ["note-reeds"]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and the pale path seemed still to remember vanished footsteps."
        }
      ],
      "audioSegments": [
        {
          "id": "segment-01",
          "text": "月の光が雲の間からほどけるころ",
          "start": 0,
          "end": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "segment-02",
          "text": "旅人",
          "start": 2,
          "end": 2
        },
        {
          "id": "segment-03",
          "text": "荒れ屋敷",
          "start": 4,
          "end": 4
        },
        {
          "id": "segment-04",
          "text": "葦は破れた門に触れ",
          "start": 6,
          "end": 6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Deep within, "
        },
        {
          "type": "annotated",
          "text": "細い灯火が消え残っていた",
          "reading": "ほそい ともしびが きえのこっていた",
          "language": "ja",
          "noteIds": ["note-lamp"]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". The traveler "
        },
        {
          "type": "annotated",
          "text": "敷居の前でためらった",
          "reading": "しきいのまえで ためらった",
          "language": "ja",
          "noteIds": ["note-hesitation"]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". No voice came, but a presence seemed to withdraw behind the curtain."
        }
      ],
      "audioSegments": [
        {
          "id": "segment-05",
          "text": "細い灯火が消え残っていた",
          "start": 1,
          "end": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "segment-06",
          "text": "敷居の前でためらった",
          "start": 3,
          "end": 3
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
